\"webchat:g-agent-master-orchestrator-cron-ed2d0b5d-fc56-42eb-a8fc-973a48024df7\",\n      \"deliveryContext\": {\n        \"channel\": \"webchat\"\n      },\n      \"updatedAt\": 1776212476764,\n      \"sessionId\": \"73a96e18-2974-41a9-ba9f-db7e47a439da\",\n      \"model\": \"AHV-Holding-DEV\",\n      \"contextTokens\": 200000,\n      \"totalTokens\": 43652,\n      \"estimatedCostUsd\": 0,\n      \"status\": \"running\",\n      \"startedAt\": 1776207735553,\n      \"childSessions\": [\n        \"agent:master-orchestrator:subagent:c2d275a5-d70a-4775-a268-fecf4708f133\",\n        \"agent:planner:subagent:63bb70ce-b5f3-48d0-a236-b6cf5d8d7922\",\n        \"agent:planner:subagent:ba49ac6d-ceff-4a9d-b3b1-7b89afdd88cc\"\n      ],\n      \"systemSent\": true,\n      \"abortedLastRun\": false,\n      \"lastChannel\": \"webchat\",\n      \"transcriptPath\": \"/root/.openclaw/agents/master-orchestrator/sessions/73a96e18-2974-41a9-ba9f-db7e47a439da.jsonl\",\n      \"messages\": [\n        {\n          \"role\": \"assistant\",\n          \"content\": [\n            {\n              \"type\": \"thinking\",\n              \"thinking\": \"Now I have the current sessions list and the last known heartbeat state. Let me compare them.\\n\\n**Last known state (heartbeat-state.json, 00:14 UTC 15 Apr):**\\n- `cron:ed2d0b5d`: running ✅\\n- `cron:e7885813`: running ✅\\n- `cron:6f3323ef`: running ✅\\n- `cron:53c5832a`: done ✅\\n- `main`: done ✅\\n- `telegram:direct:6053576134`: done ✅\\n- `telegram:group:-5163901258`: running ✅\\n\\n\\nLooking at the active sessions now, I see the QLHV monitor is still running but hasn't progressed much, the Agent Status session appears to have ended and restarted, and the DTLX monitor is still running.\\n\\nComparing this to the previous heartbeat, most sessions are in the same state. The main changes are that the QLHV 5p monitor has been running for about 20 minutes longer, and the Agent Status session has cycled back to running after being in a completed